      • failed

        boolean failed()
        Obtain failure status.
        Returns:
        true if test failed.

      • getFailure

        Throwable getFailure()
        Get exception associated to failure, if test failed.
        Returns:
        An exception object if there was a failure, null otherwise.

      • getFailureTrace

        File getFailureTrace()
        Get failure trace file.

        The file will be defined, as long as the test failed and the failed test assertion is not due related to a CSometimes hotspot.

        Returns:
        A File instance identifying a failure trace, or null if no failure trace was generated.
